Warner Bros. has released the new trailer for Christopher Nolan&#8217;s upcoming movie &#8220;Dunkirk.&#8221;The film tells the tale of British and Allied forces stranded in Dunkirk and surrounded by the German Army during World War II. It stars Tom Hardy, Mark Rylance and Kenneth Branagh, as well as former One Direction singer Harry Styles.With the tagline &#8220;At the point of crisis, at the point of annihilation, survival is victory,&#8221; the trailer sees the Allies fighting for their lives on the infamous French beach. The production is set for release on July 21, 2017.To watch the trailer, see https://youtu.be/F-eMt3SrfFU-Relaxnews